---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { t } from '../../i18n/utils';

const locale = 'en';
---

<PageLayout locale={locale} title="Terms and Conditions | Tiny House Heavens" description="Terms and conditions of Tiny House Heavens for the sale and delivery of modular tiny houses.">

  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-thh-green-50/50 to-thh-cream">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-thh-charcoal">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-thh-charcoal/50">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-thh-cream">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm space-y-8 text-thh-charcoal/80 leading-relaxed">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">1. Identity of the company</h2>
          <p>Tiny House Heavens<br/>Fort 15<br/>2860 Sint-Katelijne-Waver, Belgium<br/>VAT: BE 1007.717.063<br/>Email: info@tinyhouseheavens.com<br/>Phone: +32 465 600 263</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">2. Applicability</h2>
          <p>These terms and conditions apply to all quotes, orders and agreements concluded with Tiny House Heavens. By placing an order, the customer accepts these terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">3. Quotes and prices</h2>
          <p>All quotes are non-binding and valid for 30 days from the date of issue, unless otherwise stated. Prices are exclusive of VAT unless expressly stated otherwise. Prices may change in the event of specification or material cost changes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">4. Orders and agreements</h2>
          <p>An agreement is concluded upon written confirmation by Tiny House Heavens and receipt of the agreed deposit. The deposit amounts to a minimum of 30% of the total amount, unless otherwise agreed.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">5. Delivery</h2>
          <p>Delivery times are indicative and non-binding. Tiny House Heavens endeavours to deliver within the stated timeframe. Delays due to force majeure, changes to the order or unforeseen circumstances do not entitle the customer to compensation or cancellation.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">6. Retention of title</h2>
          <p>The delivered goods remain the property of Tiny House Heavens until full payment of all amounts due, including any interest and costs.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">7. Warranty</h2>
          <p>Tiny House Heavens provides a warranty on the construction in accordance with legal provisions. Defects must be reported in writing within 8 days of delivery. The warranty does not cover damage caused by improper use, poor maintenance or external factors.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">8. Liability</h2>
          <p>The liability of Tiny House Heavens is limited to the amount of the agreement. Indirect damage, consequential damage or lost profits will not be compensated.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">9. Cancellation</h2>
          <p>In case of cancellation by the customer after order confirmation, a cancellation fee of at least 30% of the total amount is due, to cover costs already incurred and lost profits.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-thh-charcoal mb-4">10. Disputes</h2>
          <p>Belgian law applies to all agreements. Disputes are submitted to the competent court of the district of Antwerp.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
